nodes.title: Prompt Cheat Sheet
widgets_values:
The Golden Rule

"Describe what is visible, not what is missing." AI focuses on nouns. If you write "No Hat", the AI hears "Hat". Examples:
Instead of "No jacket" Use "Sleeveless, bare arms"
Instead of "No shoes" Use "Barefoot, visible toes"
Instead of "No glasses" Use "Unobstructed eyes, clear face"
Instead of "Not looking at camera" Use "Looking away, profile shot"
Instead of "No background" Use "White background, empty space" ---

SHOT TYPES

Full body "full body, standing, head to toe"
Upper body "upper body, waist up"
Portrait "portrait, face focus, headshot"
Close up "close up, detailed face"
---

Quality Boosters

masterpiece, best quality, high quality, detailed, high resolution, sharp focus, professional ---

Lighting Terms

soft lighting: Gentle, flattering
dramatic lighting: High contrast
backlit: Light from behind
golden hour: Warm sunset tones
studio lighting: Clean, professional
rim lighting: Glowing edges
ambient lighting: Natural, soft
---

Camera Angles

from above: Looking down
from below: Looking up (dramatic)
side view: Profile
front view: Facing camera
three quarter view: Slight angle (natural)
dutch angle: Tilted, dynamic
eye level: Neutral
---

Backgrounds

simple background, white background, gradient background, blurred background, bokeh, detailed background, outdoor, indoor, bedroom, forest, city ---

Expressions

smiling: Happy
shy smile: Soft, timid
surprised: Wide eyes
angry: Furrowed brows
crying: Tears
laughing: Joyful
neutral expression: Calm
pouting: Cute grumpy
---

Pose Keywords

standing, sitting, kneeling, walking, running, hands on hips, arms crossed, looking back, waving, jumping, sleeping, hugging knees ---

Color/Mood

vibrant colors: Bright, saturated
pastel colors: Soft, muted
monochrome: Single color tone
warm tones: Orange/yellow feel
cool tones: Blue/purple feel
high contrast: Bold darks/lights
muted colors: Desaturated
---

Anime Specific

cel shaded, flat color, anime screencap, visual novel, manga style, chibi, moe, shonen style, shoujo style ---

Prompt Structure

[style], [subject], [details], [pose/action], [background], [lighting], [quality]

Example:
anime style, young girl, brown pigtails, pink pajamas, holding stuffed bunny, standing, simple bedroom background, soft lighting, high quality ---

Common Problem Fixes

Extra limbs add "simple pose" in positive, "extra limbs, mutated" in negative
Bad hands "hands behind back, hands in pockets" (hide them)
Blurry "sharp focus, detailed"
Wrong style put style words FIRST
Busy image "simple background, solo"
---

Negative Prompt Template

ugly, blurry, low quality, worst quality, deformed, extra limbs, bad anatomy, bad hands, cropped, out of frame, watermark, signature, text ---

Weighting (If Supported)

(important thing:1.3) = more emphasis
(unwanted thing:0.7) = less emphasis
